      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kata Sem-\nme bija ne-istaifita un tukcha /\nun Tuunsiba bija pahr teem Dsit-\ntumeem / un tas Deewa Gars\nliddinajahs pa Uhdens Wirfu.\n"
