      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Deews redseja/to Gaif-\nmu labbu effam / tad schihre\nDeews to Gaifmu no tahs Tuun-\nfibas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Deews nofauze to Gaif-\nmu Deena/ un to Tuunsibu fan-\nze wiꞥſch Nakts. Tad tappe no\nWatkara un Rihta ta pirma\nDeena.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Deews fazzija : Laid\ntohp Isplattijums Uhdens star-\npá/ un lat tas schihre Uhdeni no\nUhdens.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Deews darrija to Je-\nplattijumu un darrija Starpib-\nstarp to Uhdeni/ kas Isplattiju-\nma appaksha bija / un starp ta-\nUhdeni/ kas Isplattijuma *Wir-\nfii irr/ un tas notikke ta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Deews nofauze to Je-\nplattijumu/ Debbes: Tad tap-\npe no Watkara un Rihta ta oh-\ntra Deena.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Deews fazzija: Laid\nkrabjahs tas Uhdens Debbes ap-\npaksha weenâ Weeta / ka Sau-\njums tohp redsams / un tas no-\ntikke ta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Deews nofauze to\nSaufumu/ Semme/ un to Uh-\ndenu Krabjumu nofauze wiꞥſch/\nJuhra/ un DEews redseja / to\nlabbu effam.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Deews fazzija: Laid\nta Semme iswedd Saufumu un\nSahli / kas fawn Sehku nefg/\naugligus Rohkus / kas Augtus\nness pehz fawas Tautas / kam\nfawa Sehla ceefch fewis irr wirs\nSeimnes/ un tas notikke ta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ta Semme likke us-\ndiggt Sattumu un Sahli/ kas\nfawn Sehku nefg pehz fawas\nTautas/ un Rohkus / kas Aug-\ntus ness/ kam fawa Sehla ceefch\nfewis irr pehz fawas Tautas /\n"
